    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Level 2</strong> Enchantment</p>\n<p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action</p>\n<p><strong>Range:</strong> 60 feet</p>\n<p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S, M (a straight piece of iron)</p>\n<p><strong>Duration:</strong> Concentration, up to 1 minute</p>\n\nChoose a Humanoid that you can see within range. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or have the Paralyzed|XPHB condition for the duration. At the end of each of its turns, the target repeats the save, ending the spell on itself on a success.\n\n<p><strong>At Higher Levels:</strong> You can target one additional Humanoid for each spell slot level above 2.</p>",
